# 🌟 19 Unique Functionalities for Amane (Web App)

## Core Features (Enhanced)
1. Smart Reporting Form – Contextual guidance + auto-translate
2. Case Timeline Dashboard – Visual journey tracking
3. Match Me Counseling – AI + human hybrid matching
4. Resource Map – Filter by type, language, accessibility
5. Ask Question Bot – LLM + human escalation
6. Voice of Survivors – Audio + illustrated storytelling
7. Safe Circles Forums – Private, moderated peer groups
8. Healing Calendar – Virtual/in-person events
9. Wellness Games – Breathing exercises, badges
10. My Healing Tree – Visual recovery tracker
11. Whisper Mode – Zero-trace anonymous reporting
12. Careers for Change – Ethical job portal

## Additional Features
13. Family Guardian Mode – Parents report for children
14. Legal Aid Tracker – Court reminders + checklists
15. Crisis Hotline Bridge – SMS + voice call integration
16. Healing Playlist – Nature sounds, affirmations
17. Cultural Language Switcher – Amharic/Oromo/Tigrinya with context
18. Safe Exit Button – Fake website overlay + data wipe
19. Impact Dashboard – NGO/donor analytics (anonymized)

> ✅ All features designed for web accessibility, offline use, privacy-first, and cultural relevance.
